text: chaur anak pol tha brasenbae khnhom v nge v ng( brasacheak pi meakra troemotrauv) men noh ku pitabrakd nasa khnhom v nge v ng daoyokhluoneng . te brasenbae khnhom ttuol ban kar changaoulobangheanh vinh noh ku daoysaar te avei del mcheasa robsakhnhom phdal vea hi aoy khnhom . pitabrakd nasa trong mha lyy chit bamphot
